Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:25.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}絢爛奪目 不堪直視
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:31.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初始不期而至 迅如暴風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被你的眸 深深吸入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:41.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初感的衝動 因為你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想窺探 想知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}未知的你 真實的心請允許我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}數著星星的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你與我邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}兒時仰望天際
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虔誠祈禱的我已翱翔在天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中栽培夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思念孕育力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願與你攜手去往無限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}成為導航未來之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,巨獸南下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,胡鬧什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 拉萊雅到處亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,注意禮儀 這裏可是別人家的軍艦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽還沒跟古匈總監提那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…一直沒顧上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,想請Megafauna駛往Capital特區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會有這種想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真有來自宇宙的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我想Capital軍和亞美利亞必須聯合起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,和它進行對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想法確實不錯 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果宇宙臍帶教的大本營
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,願意就「來自宇宙的威脅」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,向我們進行說明 那自然好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,起碼就我個人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,從未聽法皇大人提起過這些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 為了交接光子電池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙臍帶教會定期派人登上聖波爾圖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還有荷米斯玫瑰設計圖的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,多尼爾艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,用米諾夫斯基低空飛行…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不成問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣可吃電池了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦登上大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可以找到有線電話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,通過它 我能叫來幫手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,或是領路或是保駕護航
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,180度轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,通知全員 檢查貨物固定情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,鎖定航線 宜候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:59.86,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\an7}宜候：日本幕府海军时期航海用语，宜しく候（よろしくそうろう）的简化。\N{\alpha&HFF&}宜候：{\alpha}原意是笔直前进，后作为复述命令时的用语，表示「明白」「一切正常」。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero沒駕駛員駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,會不會太暴殄天物？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？沒人開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,海洋研究所又不是駕校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,送克裏姆中尉的Armorzagan不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他們去時就做好了當誘餌的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,米克的Armorzagan擺脫了敵人的攔截
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉這時回國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是總統的施壓？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是出於作戰安排
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 這樣不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,進入伊薩尼爾大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}全員 我們即將進入Capital特區
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,伊賽拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也在監控高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,長官閣下出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我說她看起來很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒穿成這樣出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴你個秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯其實 是被領養的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？這麼說他是養子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,具體我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,危險 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,別嚇唬我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快回姐姐這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,長途電話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,話費可貴了 你懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是 這些不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.11,0:06:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是最長不許超過20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 這裏總共十一隻對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們全買走行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,價錢好商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊池塘裏的魚也是賣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,稍…稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿計算器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！啾啾咪不能吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,姬蘭小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,她誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}姬蘭小姐 你是護士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}應該更理解拉萊雅才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我家貝魯利和艾達·蘇爾坎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長 讓船開穩一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,地面上的米諾夫斯基飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可比在宇宙裏當海盜難多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真的打算在這裏做彈射實驗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,需要能在各種環境下出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,無人狀態下彈射能用自動駕駛返航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被撒了米諾夫斯基粒子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,會像斷了線的風箏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼搖晃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,低速航行容易受風影響
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙戰艦之類 原本是把人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是把人類推向滅亡的技術象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這條航線真的能突破Capital軍的警戒線？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才電話裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經讓Capital衛隊趕來接應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,應該可以避開軍隊耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要船員瞭望時做好戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還在船上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔的運營長官也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏是南邊的伊薩尼爾大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是敵人領地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼敵人和敵人領地！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏是我們的故鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 非常抱歉 諾蕾朵·納古小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 多…多謝你直言不諱的 問…問候方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,受寵若驚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,受寵若驚 受寵若驚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}打開格納庫 注意強風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,隨時歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒 Montero和Gehennam可以彈射了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼 哈朋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想讓那架無人的Gehennam出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,調查部的昆珀·盧西達上校？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 他應該對荷米斯玫瑰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那是安赫爾瀑布嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:51.01,Default1,,0,0,0,,{\an7}安赫爾瀑布：又名天使瀑布（Angel Falls），委內瑞拉與圭亞那高原密林深處的世界最高瀑布。\N{\alpha&HFF&}安赫爾瀑布：{\alpha}1937年美國探險家詹姆斯·安赫爾對其進行考察時墜機身亡，為紀念他命名。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這樣的附近有許多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這也叫瀑布 真讓人笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧這些平頂山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,才能躲過Capital塔的雷達監視
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在正規軍駕駛員面前班門弄斧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,動作真快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是正規軍駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以！史堤厄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,現在加速會被雷達發現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,遵…遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,被撒了米諾夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是些好戰份子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,史堤厄 把他們甩得遠遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是 長官！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是Capital軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不怪你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,變形了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那夠不成傷害 又來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯…我這人真沒用！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,笨手笨腳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是上次的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 機動堡壘？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不想在這裏不期而遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝從絕望中拯救我 G-Self！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,開始加速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gehennam別出動 敗家！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero出動！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,開始加速
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Montero的敵我識別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,讓攝像機來完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,能用標槍 這可是你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,準備 走起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,又是它！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,無人駕駛？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這會讓你露出破綻！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不能放跑他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大勢已去麼 芭拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,援軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看見人讓我怎麼下得了手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,別亂來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,視野…看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,滑過了 回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,點剎車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,剎車！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上返回Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍作忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我冷靜一下再進艙內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,優先向昆珀上校請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,逃離Megafauna！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神 就當到了Capital塔腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,機動戰士保持戰鬥戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,米諾夫斯基粒子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,正在消散 所以讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fry-Schop也保持戰備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self的技術真爛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,別把甲板踩出坑來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？貝魯這麼菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是打仗累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠順利抵達這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也歸功於長官的作戰計劃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…因為Capital衛隊和軍隊性格不合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼 盧安先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,請問長官在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是凱爾貝斯·悠教官閣下？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 貝魯利·賽納姆同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是跳級生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這情況看來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不像是奪回了G-Self的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,凱爾貝斯 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你認得出剛才襲擊這艘船的F-Rag嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是Capital軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看見了 但在下不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利學員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,當上亞美利亞軍的駕駛員了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞軍不肯給我中尉軍銜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以還是Capital衛隊的學員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那位如果我沒記錯的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是海盜小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝您的掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,長官親自來電 當然得來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我還帶了點偽裝 幫這艘船躲避探測
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快到目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,請跟住前方的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能做到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？你跟誰說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼長官…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital衛隊的職員都像他那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,更準確地說 是宇宙臍帶教的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那個宇宙臍帶教…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼小？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,跟數字給人的印象完全不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能控制姿態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,開始測量 伊賽拉也來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,收起翅片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fin put back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,測算距離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,懸停下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}5 4…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,穿過頂梁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 看準時機著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好 關閉懸停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,躲進哪裏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裏不都一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,凱爾貝斯 見到長官了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他們先把全新的光子電池
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和壓縮空氣水球運來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,父親 看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是大四葉草
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我家就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,來住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,家？住？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以過夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那些貨車是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,配給全世界的光子電池
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,全部由那些貨車運往空港
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦電池上了貨車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽的工作就算完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,直接飛過去不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Rag不可以接近大四葉草上空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍的人可從不遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍更像某種暴力自衛團
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,並沒有經過我的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,用得慣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}別騎在Shank上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}來吧 來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}來吧 別只知道工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是富足帶來的後果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔的勤務工作十分辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,每週一次的放鬆是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這是艾達·蘇爾坎小姐的ID卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,古匈·蘇爾坎先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有勞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,週末沒有監視？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是在開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,上校！我可以叫男友來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,說過請便！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,讓面具先去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我想安排面具與茹甘司令見面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 要等過完週末？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼Capital軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,地球人還真配得上被歸入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可以任其滅絕的動物種群！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧 聽聞長官外出公幹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛返回嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是 驚聞宇宙中禍事將至
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,特來請教法皇陛下實情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？是諾蕾朵·納古小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是否安好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 托法皇大人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那便好 願長此以往平平安安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔不會受到任何人的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,父親想知道的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是否會有來自宇宙的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,縱觀R.C世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:37.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an7}R.C世紀：Regild Century（重鍍世紀）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,正因宇宙臍帶教慈悲為懷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital塔才得以運轉至今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 宇宙臍帶教的教義中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,並未提及Capital塔與宇宙人的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,每天清晨醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都必須從說明空氣的成分開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,難道閣下認為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,光子電池是太空中自然形成的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,無法對光子電池進行分解或維修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,強行為之 會導致爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才被歸入禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,才助長了惡意壟斷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們亞美利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,為從Capital塔的壟斷中解放地球…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這種想法才是最大的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,韋米特·賽納姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到長官已經凱旋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,昆珀上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,您週末的休假呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇爾坎總監為什麼也在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,想請教昆珀上校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,關於荷米斯玫瑰設計圖的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,您知情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,多麼夢幻的名稱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,突然拜訪 萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,調查部的頭頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍的幕後主謀竟然也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利·賽納姆候補生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐也來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨 父親拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:21:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達·蘇爾坎！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小心摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦被Capital軍盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,僅憑艾達小姐個人的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.85,0:24:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Megafauna不可能脫險
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.45,0:24:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,最後之所以成功
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.23,0:24:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是因為G-Self高機動背包的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.92,0:24:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因為我的奇思妙想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 G之復國
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.40,0:24:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,逃離特區
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,見識我的天才吧！
